name: BODY N2
description:
This will be the collection of art that exalt all types of female bodies. 
Woman don’t have to hide their body and their sexuality. Sexuality is just one of the many feminine aspects, and to hide and be ashamed of it means not fully accept yourself. One of the feminine arts is the ability to be different, and I think it's gorgeous.🤍

Especially, when you consider how beautiful female body is by nature. Seriously, it's just a work of art and it's not surprise that female bodies have been inspiring the most famous artists for so many centuries - Renoir, Van Gogh, Dali, Modigliani….

In the end, if you delve into history, it becomes clear that women and sexuality always walks hand in hand, and this is more our strength than weakness.
